The Middle East & Africa is gradually emerging as a niche market with investments in semiconductor technology parks and electronics manufacturing. Although relatively smaller in scale, expanding industrial diversification initiatives are expected to create new opportunities over the coming years.
South America continues to experience moderate growth supported by expanding electronics manufacturing activities and increasing demand for semiconductor packaging solutions across automotive and consumer electronics industries.

